{"tid":1170925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發表批評川普言論 美國猶他州法官停職6個月","createTime":"2019-05-25T10:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T11:26:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"debd9a106fd8afce950c1cadcb19a95d1928a379","tid":1170925,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"（中央社洛杉磯25日綜合外電報導）美國一名法官因發表詆毀總統川普的言論，遭當地最高法院停職6個月且不得支領薪水，他曾批評川普「沒有能力治國且政治無能」。<br />\n<br />\n猶他州（Utah）最高法院本週稍早認為，法官關維斌（Michael Kwan）的行為違反法官行為準則，且傷害司法信譽。<br />\n<br />\n最高法院在一份19頁意見書表示：「關維斌法官的行為，損害作為一名公正、獨立、有尊嚴且謙恭有禮法官的名聲，對於他服務的部門百害而無一利 。」<br />\n<br />\n對於關維斌在社群媒體臉書（Facebook）和領英（LinkedIn）發表有關川普的言論，最高法院表示這些言論「充斥粗鄙、有時是下流的批評」。<br />\n<br />\n川普2017年1月20日宣誓就職時，關維斌寫道：「觀迎就任。你會堅持己見且花4年時間破壞我們國家聲譽和世界地位？&hellip;你會繼續展現你在治國和政治上的無能？」<br />\n<br />\n關維斌1個月後在另一則貼文寫道：「歡迎法西斯主義者開始接管（美國）。」<br />\n<br />\n最高法院指出，關維斌曾在一場法庭聽審中，批評川普的移民和稅收政策。<br />\n<br />\n當時一名被告在法庭上告訴關維斌，打算收到退稅後繳交他的法院罰金，關維斌則告訴被告：「你知道我們已經有一位新總統，你認為我們有辦法把錢拿回來嗎？祈禱可能就是答案。」<br />\n<br />\n關維斌說：「因為他（川普）剛簽署命令要開始築牆，他沒有錢退稅，所以你認為你今年能拿到退稅，嗯，也許會，也許不會。但不要擔心，富人將能減稅，所以如果你收入超過50萬美元，你就能減稅。」<br />\n<br />\n過去20年在泰勒斯維爾市（Taylorsville）擔任法官的關維斌，曾發表政治相關的不當言論且脾氣不好。他承認自己行為不符合法官身份，但他辯稱，在法庭上的政治言論只是搏君一笑，且認為停職處分等同侵犯他的言論自由。（譯者：葉俐緯/核稿：陳彥鈞）1080525<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201905250138.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201905250138.aspx&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62JFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=a4e170c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201905250138.aspx</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/afs-prod/media/media:72b521eb7a104b02a7d76eb8abf7c1d7/2000.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fafs-prod%2Fmedia%2Fmedia%3A72b521eb7a104b02a7d76eb8abf7c1d7%2F2000.jpeg&h=dd147d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/wireStory/utah-judge-suspended-making-anti-trump-comments-63258536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2FwireStory%2Futah-judge-suspended-making-anti-trump-comments-63258536&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62JFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=82a187ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/wireStory/utah-judge-suspended-making-anti-trump-comments-63258536</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apnews.com/8b187c589b3d42589ab89b8afc05356e/gallery/media:72b521eb7a104b02a7d76eb8abf7c1d7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apnews.com%2F8b187c589b3d42589ab89b8afc05356e%2Fgallery%2Fmedia%3A72b521eb7a104b02a7d76eb8abf7c1d7&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62JFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=d9df2da3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apnews.com/8b187c589b3d42589ab89b8afc05356e/gallery/media:72b521eb7a104b02a7d76eb8abf7c1d7</a>"},{"pid":"ae1cbf6bace8208302ab2382cda89649d32ce30e","tid":1170925,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbd045860a16f71613200b789fe147ac070ac56e","tid":1170925,"uid":3457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ae1cbf6bace8208302ab2382cda89649d32ce30e","tid":1170925,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"如果係中國？ <br />\n個法官抑鬱左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6cfe9e3a685360cac89ea688fd0553fe2220da","tid":1170925,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"又係d支那間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0dc2923fe2851fc7f9e2b715d1514dbfd04c2d","tid":1170925,"uid":99856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:47:54.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f0cf625a37f02d30890e26582d85d5ea07f065","tid":1170925,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3f6cfe9e